{
  "stem": "19969.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 101.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "My executive officer took one prong.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "I took the other.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "And then we just smashed whatever we ran into with a-- we had such tremendous firepower.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "The Germans, there's only-- put up-- they would blow up bridges and defend places like that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "But we had so much firepower that-- and we had the engineers coming up, bridging the rivers for us in fast, fast order.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "The American Corps of Engineers was remarkably organized for helping the combat troops.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And they could put a bridge across a very large river in a fairly short time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And so wherever we ran into problems, we-- I'd get infantry across the river to protect the engineers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "And they would come up and put their bridge across.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And then I could get my tanks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "Well, this continued in for several days.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And we were cutting off, oh, like, 50 miles a day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "That is, until my tanks ran out of gas, actually.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And they would have to stop and refuel.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "Until-- and on the evening of April 28, 1945, I was about 30 miles or a little less from Munich.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "So I geared up to make the attack towards Munich, got my tanks refueled by midnight.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And we were going to take off the daylight.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "I'm running into very little German opposition, just a few roadblocks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And that took us, oh, usually 20, 30 minutes to wipe out what was in our way.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And then we were on our way again.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "Well, and that night, I got-- I got a word over, over our radio system that the Dachau Concentration Camp was in our zone of action the next day.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "And the-- this information was sent to all units, not just to me, all units in the Seventh Army.",
      "word_count": 19
    }
  ],
